{
    "key": 63855,
    "messages": [
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_WakeIntro",
            "en_US": [
                "Welcome!\n",
                "I don\u2019t get challenged very often!\r",
                "The glory you are now beholding is\n",
                "the Pastoria Gym Leader!\r",
                "That\u2019s right, I\u2019m Crasher Wake!\r",
                "My Pok\u00e9mon were toughened up by\n",
                "stormy white waters!\r",
                "They\u2019ll take everything you can throw\n",
                "at them and then pull you under!\r",
                "Victory will be ours!\n",
                "Come on, let\u2019s get it done!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_BeatWake",
            "en_US": [
                "It seems the undertow pulled me\n",
                "under...\r",
                "But I had a great time battling\n",
                "with you!\r",
                "You\u2019ve earned this!\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_WakeReveiveFenBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0} received\n",
                "the Fen Badge from Wake!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_WakeExplainFenBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "You need that Fen Badge to use the\n",
                "hidden move Surf outside of battle.\r",
                "This is a special reward from me in\n",
                "recognition of your team\u2019s power.\r"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_WakeExplainTM55",
            "en_US": [
                "That {STRVAR_1 8, 0, 0} contains the\n",
                "move {STRVAR_1 6, 1, 0}.\r",
                "It inflicts double the damage on\n",
                "targets with less than half their\f",
                "HP left.\r",
                "Use it to end battles decisively!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_WakeAfterbadge",
            "en_US": [
                "The styles of battling and winning\n",
                "are as widely varied as Trainers are.\r",
                "Do you want to know how I battle?\n",
                "I battle so I can say I had fun at\f",
                "the end, whether I win or lose!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_GymGuideBeforebadge",
            "en_US": [
                "The Gym Leader Wake... Uh, I mean\n",
                "Crasher Wake, is a master of\f",
                "Water-type Pok\u00e9mon.\r",
                "I\u2019d say you\u2019ve got guts if you try\n",
                "to face down Water types with Fire-\f",
                "or Ground-type Pok\u00e9mon!\r",
                "But that part I\u2019ll leave up to you!\n",
                "Go and have some good battles!"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_GymGuideAfterbadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Oh! {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}!\n",
                "You\u2019ve beaten the Gym Leader!\r",
                "So, how was it?\r",
                "Did you enjoy your battle against\n",
                "Wake... I mean Crasher Wake?\r",
                "Sure, winning is important, but\n",
                "don\u2019t forget to have fun, too!\r",
                "I think Wake... I mean Crasher Wake,\n",
                "showed you what I mean by fun."
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_GymStatueBeforeBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Pastoria City Pok\u00e9mon Gym\n",
                "Leader: Crasher Wake\r",
                "Certified Trainers:\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "PastoriaGym_Text_GymStatueAfterBadge",
            "en_US": [
                "Pastoria City Pok\u00e9mon Gym\n",
                "Leader: Crasher Wake\r",
                "Certified Trainers:\n",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}\f",
                "{STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "GymExit_Text_MustDefeatLeader_PastoriaGym",
            "en_US": [
                "You can\u2019t leave until you\n",
                "defeat the Gym Leader!\r"
            ]
        }
    ]
}